HEADWORD: Soreness
<hw>Sore"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state
of being sore; tenderness; painfully; <as>as, the <ex>soreness</ex> of a
wound; the <ex>soreness</ex> of an affliction</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

